00:47:42.520 --> 00:47:51.239
important because even if we could cut, you know, 5% of that, it becomes a good hard dollar ROI.

00:47:51.879 --> 00:47:58.840
And the second piece is looking at things like risk, like when you have like an activity like

00:47:58.840 --> 00:48:05.239
diving, you do have a lot of occupational risk. And we're actually able to tie, you know, what

00:48:06.600 --> 00:48:11.159
the occupational risk is and how it compares to other activities that we do at the plant.

00:48:11.159 --> 00:48:17.080
So it allows us to kind of capture both the hard savings and also the qualitative

00:48:17.080 --> 00:48:21.639
software savings. And again, just starting with a big target of project that,

00:48:22.840 --> 00:48:25.639
you know, is targeting a big budget, I think it's important.

